              "text" : "USE [PLHS]\nGO\n\ndeclare @yesterday date\nset @yesterday = (select BusinessDay from Calendar where CurrentDate = cast(getdate() as date)) \n-- TODO: Set parameter values here.\n\n\nINSERT INTO [dbo].[tbl_ssis_utility]\n ([To]\n      ,[Subject]\n      ,[body]\n      ,[ReceiveDate]\n      ,[SendDate]\n      ,[BodyFormat]\n      ,[CC]\n\t  )\nSELECT\n 'greg.wilkinson@wellsfargo.com;michael.dematos@wellsfargo.com;sergio.dsilva@wellsfargo.com;tim.kemen@wellsfargo.com;riyaz.sheikh@wellsfargo.com'\n ,'New/Re-Activated EM/HA vulnerability Alert'\n ,\n \ncast('The following list of Emergency/HA CombID have been identified as not being included in the pervious days Extract, validate with iTracker History\n\n' +string_agg('<br>'+a.CombID,',</br>')+'</br>' as ntext) \nas body\n,GETDATE() as receivedate \n,null as senddate\n,2 as bodyformat\n,'ethan.a.baker@wellsfargo.com;mark.bray@wellsfargo.com' as CC\n\nFROM \n\ntbl_VulnActive_Daily_Static a \nleft outer join \niTracker_Active_SN_CIO b on a.combid = b.combid and cast(b.ImportDate as date) =@yesterday\n\nWHERE Rating_Summary ='Emergency/HA'  and b.CombID is null"
